choices.text: where will I spend my food allowance of 100 crowns (or around $4,5)? Before I’ll reach 25, I’ve set myself some questions regarding my future (expecting that at that point I’ll be more mature and able to make coherent decisions). Will I be able to travel the world, help people or will I be just another disappointment of my family? In a wall of thoughts, I accidentally found some advices about “croudfunding” that through internet you could raise some money for some ‘good’ purposes. And I thought – “Hey, if I am not the one who’s going to take the actions needed to help others, how can I blame others who think the same?” So 2 years ago I decided to fuck up this New Year’s resolutions bullshit and to make some changes in the surrounding myself. To my surprise, it was the best decision in my life. My world
